window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Just when you think you understand life, an elf throws you a curveball.</p> <p>Zaena has to deal with a recalcitrant elf who won't listen to reason and doesn't care about his people or hers.</p> <p>He is out for himself.</p> <p>Unfortunately for him, his gang headquarters is smack-dab on top of a location Zaena needs.</p> <p>To further complicate matters, the gang wars in San Francisco have attracted the attention of humans who might know too much for Zaena's safety.</p> <p>Will she be able to negotiate her way out of this situation with words or power?</p>"; 
